
<head>
    <!-- Custom CSS -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/style-index.css" />
</head>

<!-- Landing section-->
<section class="landing">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <!-- Text -->
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="text">
                    In recycling <br />new era of crypto
                    <span class="gradient-text">RECYCLE COIN</span>
                </div>
                <div class="buttons">
                    <a asp-area="" asp-controller="Authentication" asp-action="Register" class="btn btn-primary">Get Started</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Image -->
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <img src="~/images/globe.png" alt="globe-img" class="w-100" />
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Earn Coin section-->
<section class="earn-coin">
    <div class="container">
        <h3>Get started in just a few minutes</h3>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-4 positions">
                <div class="card d-block p-3">
                    <img src="~/images/signup.png" alt="sign up" />
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h4>Sign Up</h4>
                        <p>
                            Earn Recycle Coins, then store them securely in your wallet or
                            easily send them to your friends
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 positions">
                <div class="card d-block p-3">
                    <img src="~/images/wallet.png" alt="wallet" />
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h4>Recycle</h4>
                        <p>
                            Earn money and protect the environment by bringing recyclable
                            materials to our recycling centers
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 positions">
                <div class="card d-block p-3">
                    <img src="~/images/earn.png" alt="earn" />
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h4>Earn Coin</h4>
                        <p>
                            Sign up for your free Recycle wallet and follow our easy
                            process to create your profile
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- About section -->
<section class="about" id="about">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row info-1">
            <!-- Image -->
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <img src="~/images/tradingtools.png"
                     alt="About us"
                     class="w-100" />
            </div>

            <!-- Text -->
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="text-information">
                    <h5>Let's introduce ourselves</h5>
                    <p>
                        We believe that there should be no such thing as waste in the
                        world. Together we keep our environment clean by developing new
                        solutions and new uses for recyclables.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Client opinion section -->
<section class="client-area"></section>

<!-- Support questions -->
<section class="support-questions" id="support">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <!-- Text -->
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="text-information">
                    <h5>SUPPORT</h5>
                    <h4>Frequently asked questions</h4>

                    <div class="accordion" id="accordionExample">
                        <div class="accordion-item">
                            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingOne">
                                <button class="accordion-button"
                                        type="button"
                                        data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                                        data-bs-target="#collapseOne"
                                        aria-expanded="true"
                                        aria-controls="collapseOne">
                                    What is the main purpose of Recycle Coin?
                                </button>
                            </h2>
                            <div id="collapseOne"
                                 class="accordion-collapse collapse show"
                                 aria-labelledby="headingOne"
                                 data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
                                <div class="accordion-body">
                                    <strong>It is a decentralized cryptocurrency.</strong> It
                                    is open source software; identified by encrypted and
                                    anonymous codes. As it uses peer to peer (P2P) technology,
                                    it enables all kinds of financial transactions to be
                                    recorded easily between peers in a secure environment.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="accordion-item">
                            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingTwo">
                                <button class="accordion-button collapsed"
                                        type="button"
                                        data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                                        data-bs-target="#collapseTwo"
                                        aria-expanded="false"
                                        aria-controls="collapseTwo">
                                    How can I convert my recycle items into Recycle Coins?
                                </button>
                            </h2>
                            <div id="collapseTwo"
                                 class="accordion-collapse collapse"
                                 aria-labelledby="headingTwo"
                                 data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
                                <div class="accordion-body">
                                    Recycling objects brought by the user are entered into the
                                    system by the operator, and points are added to the
                                    address of the person who brings the waste.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="accordion-item">
                            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingThree">
                                <button class="accordion-button collapsed"
                                        type="button"
                                        data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                                        data-bs-target="#collapseThree"
                                        aria-expanded="false"
                                        aria-controls="collapseThree">
                                    Why is recycling necessary?
                                </button>
                            </h2>
                            <div id="collapseThree"
                                 class="accordion-collapse collapse"
                                 aria-labelledby="headingThree"
                                 data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
                                <div class="accordion-body">
                                    By recycling, we protect both nature and our resources. As
                                    a result of recycling plastic packaging waste, oil savings
                                    can be achieved. By recycling metal packaging, we can
                                    protect our natural areas from deterioration.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Image -->
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <img src="~/images/faq.png" alt="Asked questions" class="w-100" />
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>